              h2 Taekwondo Lesson

              p
                img.mugshot.img-thumbnail.img-responsive(src='/images/good-idea-plan.jpg', alt='Good Idea Schedule', title='Good Idea Schedule')
                | Last month I went to watch a friend teach his weekly Taekwondo class. A couple of the younger students
